Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Never Land (永无之乡)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「狮牙」 你也还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:32.00,sp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110}注: 狮牙 (Dandelion) - AX派遣执行官里昂的代号 他被判处千年徒刑\N以任务来缩短其刑期的方式而替AX工作.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次能减多少年的刑期？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七千三百天 二十年左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十年？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 是什么事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从上个月开始 在艾伯塔恩的近海区域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,频繁发生吸血鬼袭击船舶的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从现场回收了某个人的遗骸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:09.10,sp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110}注: 妖精 - 吸血鬼的一种\N藉由展开在背部的副肺排出空气 进行高速飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在吸血鬼当中 这也是稀有的品种呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查结果证明 他并非是先天性的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是遭到后天「转向」的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:16.40,sp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110}注: 转向 - 被吸血的受害者 有机会成为另一个吸血鬼 这种人称之为「转向者」\N但发生的机率不到0.1% 是种极为罕见的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 是被制造的吸血鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他原本是个孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像曾被这个人收养过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆士．巴雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦迪尼姆大学医学部前部长 艾伯塔恩的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经引退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在领地的小岛上 经营着小规模的孤儿院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是提不起干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种跟小孩子有关的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到小岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂 冒烟了 烟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 真的不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为租金很便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 在警告灯没亮之前都不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩之前要先帮田地浇水施肥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿做不也一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一起玩捉迷藏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连卡莉也这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙 那些家伙要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 我来打倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负温迪的家伙 由我来打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉 其它人拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得坚强一点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能着陆的更稳当点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的小命还在就该谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去的时候怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正无线电也坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 我们遇难了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主啊 如果要我承受这样的考验的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如干脆死了算…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人快滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这个岛上的人吗 你父母呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴雷教授果然如传闻般地喜欢小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样照顾着从各地收养来的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我也是被领养的孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要砂糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加十三份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十三份？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但被你们所救 还请我喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是茶叶好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 果然还是泡茶的功夫好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴雷教授不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这里只有你们几个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做菜和洗衣服的话 单靠我们也就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是想问神父一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…埃布尔•奈特罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇厅…国务圣省
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特务分室…AX
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 神父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AX的人来这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼、袭击船舶、处理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自白剂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来杀我们的吗 此外还有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴雷教授在什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有意识嘛 剂量太少了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾啊 神父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法见到巴雷教授了 永远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经得到了 绝不让大人妨碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是属于小孩们的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输给大叔了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是大叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 小孩子怎么能赢过大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会变强给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得比大叔更强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变强了后 准备干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护温迪 保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温迪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我不该笑你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强或弱不能拿来当借口 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己现在全部的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去保护心爱的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够做到这点的话 你就是一个男子汉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 你的素质也不差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再努力个四、五年的话 肯定行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 我也能变得像大叔那么强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 能变得仅次于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉在你这么兴奋的时候打断你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我把埃布尔叫来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个看起来笨笨的眼镜神父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是「失败作」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以认为自己不能像成功品那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我会努力的 努力成为大人 然后变强的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败作？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手真是意外的敏捷啊 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省了我找你们的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 让我们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢这么做 可恶的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高周波吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 我来救你了 跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很讨厌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个留在这里会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这里吧 带我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一样 不能成功「转向」而死掉的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「转向」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用人工方式制造吸血鬼 是巴雷教授的实验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被输血 在肚子和背上植入奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授对大家做尽残酷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是温迪 每天都被欺负到哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家都讨厌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要变成大人 我要变强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变强后 就可以保护温迪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是「失败作」的我 温迪也总是温柔地对待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得 你要到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直当个乖小孩的话 本来是可以好好相处的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你不同 他并没有逃避自己的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是了不起的男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不允许你污辱他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小仙子系统」 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.70,sp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110}注: 小仙子系统 - 在兵器"沉默之声"后被延伸开发出来的战术统御系统\N由"主人"与"下属"两种系统架构所组成.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的合作 是怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众人即我 我即是众人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家以我的意志来行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧 就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 喜欢说场面话的神父
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微铃系统被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人与下属式的战术统御系统
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是透过那个钟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你的思考传递给其它妖精 并进行控制
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要破坏掉钟 系统就瘫痪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂 你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的任务是逮捕巴雷教授
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及消灭所有袭击船舶的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不用杀掉他们啊 逮捕起来不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做反而更加残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是「人为转向」成功的珍贵例子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:54.00,sp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110}注: 人为转向 - 使用违反自然法则的方式\N强制"转向"这个现象 并制造出"妖精"的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往后几百年里 将会被当作人体实验的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果觉得残酷的话 就祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们AX也是允许祈祷的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不允许怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 不要杀温迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得 给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温迪其实是很善良的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事 都只是照医生的命令做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得 已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在「永无之乡」的时间已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:51.00,sp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110}注: Never Land (永无之乡) - 典故出自著名童话"Peter Pan"里\N主角彼得潘所居住的岛名 又称为"梦幻岛"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你不是很强吗 救救温迪 救救大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼得 拜托你 不要再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什么大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜牲 就我一个当坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起 彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来怎么办 埃布尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经有办法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能说没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在永无之乡岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突袭了巴雷教授进行非法实验的藏身处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没能确认教授的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是全灭了吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 公费清单中有一张奇怪的收据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说租了一艘货船什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货物的目的地则是艾伯塔恩的伦迪尼姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金额也很庞大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:21:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是什么来着的 埃布尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是、是什么来着的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那么这就不能判定是公费开销了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这将成为你们的个人开支
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收款单将会转交给你们 请做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的金额 我实在是、实在是拿不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是吃牢饭的 哪有钱啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋 怎么不先想好借口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂你才是 一副信心十足的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我放心地以为你已经想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不考虑正是我的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我怎么会觉得你有考虑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 眼镜男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你刚才叫我笨蛋了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是孩子气啊 两个人都是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.80,0:23:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 第八话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silent Noise (沉默之声)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.30,0:23:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别给我错过了
